column7: Data usage: The information collected in the form above will be used to provide free copies of 'Diamond the game'. Postcodes will be anonymised and used for Diamond’s reporting on the distribution of the game, the remaining information shall be deleted following shipment of your game. It will not be used for any other purpose. Please note that the information in this form is hosted by a third-party service, provided by Vroman Systems, Inc. (“Formsite”).
